		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T4F</code>: Visualisation</h1>
		Work about visual representations and interaction: graphical modelling, visual syntaxes, diagramming, visual editors, visualisation-driven analytics of language artefacts, and human-facing rendering of language structures/behaviour. Usability studies of such tools are primarily <a href="t5h.html">T5H</a>.
